Cantrips				KEY:Cantrips ~ Drake Tamer		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality		DESC:You have learned a number of cantrips, or0-level spells. They are cast like any other spells, but they may be cast any number of times per day. Cantrips prepared using 1st- and higher-level spell slots, due to metamagic feats, for example, consume spell slots as normal.		SOURCEPAGE:pg.18
Dragon Friend			KEY:Dragon Friend ~ Drake Tamer	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Extraordinary	DEFINE:DragonFriendBonus|0	DESC:You know how to deal with all types of dragons, adding %1 to all Charisma-based skill checks when interacting with creatures of the dragon type.|DragonFriendBonus		SOURCEPAGE:pg.18		BONUS:VAR|DragonFriendBonus|CL/2
Drake Companion			KEY:Drake Companion ~ Drake Tamer	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Extraordinary		DEFINE:DrakeLevel|0	FOLLOWERS:Drake Companion|1	COMPANIONLIST:Drake Companion|RACETYPE=Dragon	DESC:You have gained a drake companion.
Empathic Link			KEY:Empathic Link ~ Drake Tamer	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Supernatural.Communicate		DESC:You have an empathic link with your drake companion out to one mile. This link can communicate feelings and emotions but not complex or coherent thoughts or sensory input. The drake tamer has the same connection to an item or place that her companion does.
Share Spells			KEY:Share Spells ~ Drake Tamer	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Supernatural	DESC:You may cast a spell with a target of “you” on your drake companion (as a touch spell) instead of on yourself. You may cast spells on the drake even if the spells do not normally affect creatures of the dragon type.	SOURCEPAGE:pg.18
Drake Flank				KEY:Drake Flank ~ Drake Tamer	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialAttack.Extraordinary	DESC:You effectively team up with her drake companion, gaining an additional +2 bonus to hit when you flanks with your drake. The drake is also considered to have an effective reach of 5 feet, regardless of its size, when it is flanking with you.		SOURCEPAGE:pg.18
