Deliver Touch Spells	KEY:Deliver Touch Spells ~ Drake Tamer	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Supernatural	DEFINE:DeliverTouchSpellDuration|0	DESC:You can imbue your drake to deliver spells with a range of touch. If you and your drake are in physical contact when you cast the spell, you can designate your companion as “carrying” the spell. The drake carries the spell for %1 rounds and can deliver the touch spell just as you would. If you casts another spell before the touch is delivered, the touch spell dissipates.|DeliverTouchSpellDuration	SOURCEPAGE:pg.18		BONUS:VAR|DeliverTouchSpellDuration|CHA
Drake Feature			KEY:Drake Feature ~ Drake Tamer		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Supernatural	DEFINE:DrakeFeatureBonus|0	DESC:You take on some of the aspects of your companion. You may spend %1 feature points on yourself but only to duplicate an ability possessed by your companion.|DrakeFeatureBonus		SOURCEPAGE:pg.18	BONUS:ABILITYPOOL|Drake Feature|DrakeFeatureBonus
Drake Devotion			KEY:Drake Devotion ~ Drake Tamer	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality,Extraordinary	DESC:You gains a morale bonus to Will saves against enchantment spells and effects.		SOURCEPAGE:pg.18	BONUS:CHECKS|Will|4|TYPE=Morale
Drake Apportation		KEY:Drake Apportation ~ Drake Tamer	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Supernatural	DESC:You can magically cross long distances with your drake companion. This ability requires line of sight and works exactly like the dimension door spell, save that the drake tamer or her drake companion must arrive within five feet of the other. Alternatively, this ability can transpose the drake tamer and her companion, provided there is room at the respective destinations. At 18th level, this ability functions exactly like greater teleport, with the added ability to exchange places.
Drake Telepathy			KEY:Drake Telepathy ~ Drake Tamer	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Supernatural.Communicate	DESC:The drake tamer learns to improve on her empathic contact with her companion. At 9th level, she can communicate with her drake telepathically up to 1 mile away. At 14th level, this ability has an unlimited range, as long as both are on the same plane.	SOURCEPAGE:pg.19
Scry on Drake			KEY:Scry on Drake ~ Drake Tamer		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Supernatural	DESC:You can scry on any of your drake companions (as if casting the scrying spell) a total of twice per day.	SOURCEPAGE:pg.19
Drake Diplomat			KEY:Drake Diplomat ~ Drake Tamer	CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Extraordinary	DEFINE:DrakeDiplomatDC|0	DESC:A creature of the dragon type must make a Will save (DC %1) to attack you, as long as you do not attack the dragon.	SOURCEPAGE:pg.19	BONUS:VAR|DrakeDiplomatDC|10+(HD/2)+CHA
Dual Drake				KEY:Dual Drake ~ Drake Tamer		CATEGORY:Special Ability	TYPE:SpecialQuality.Supernatural	DESC:You share a complete connection with your drake. As a standard action, you can assume the drake’s shape, copying all of its abilities. Your Strength, Dexterity, and Constitution scores change to match the base scores of you drake. The new form absorbs your clothing and gear. Any items with continuous effects continue to function in the new form. You gains your drake’s abilities while losing your own natural attacks and all racial traits, with the exception of bonus feats, skills, and languages. You can keep this form for %1 minutes per day. This duration need not be consecutive, but it must be spent in 1-minute increments. Ending this effect requires a free action.|DrakeTamerLVL	SOURCEPAGE:pg.19


